review_blob: Nice sweet smell with a hint of grapefruit was pretty excited to take a drink. Poured into a light head and a reddish goldfish color to it. But I was upset with the flavor which it lacks pretty bland.

Well I found this brew at my local liquor store.. and see it is made in my home town so I decided to get a 6 pack of bottles. Its pours a light golden brown it smells grainy and a little malty. The taste is kind of bland. Seems like it will be a brew to have once in awhile but I wont be going out of my way getting any.

Lets just say for the price of the beer its worth it. Nice thick head sweet apple taste almost could be a lager. This is a case I could grab and bring out to the fish house and everyone will enjoy ! Cheers!

beer_brewer_name: Leinenkugel Brewing Company (Tenth & Blake Beer Co.)
review_blob: Nice crisp citrus taste. Seems like its a brew that I could enjoy year around.. but you wouldnt be catching me having a half case of these
